      "12": "de tauta dusin ex autwn peripatousin efanerwqh en etera morfh poreuomenois eis agron",
      "13": "apelqontes aphggeilan tois loipois oude ekeinois episteusan",
      "14": "de anakeimenois autois tois endeka efanerwqh kai wneidisen thn apistian autwn kai sklhrokardian oti tois qeasamenois auton eghgermenon ouk episteusan",
      "15": "eipen autois poreuqentes eis ton kosmon apanta khruxate to euaggelion pash th ktisei",
