      "3": "eporeuonto pantes apografesqai ekastos eis thn eautou polin",
      "4": "de kai iwshf apo ths galilaias ek polews nazareq eis thn ioudaian eis polin daueid htis kaleitai bhqleem dia to einai auton ex oikou kai patrias daueid",
      "5": "sun mariam th emnhsteumenh autw oush egkuw",
