      "10": "eipen autois o aggelos mh fobeisqe idou gar euaggelizomai umin caran megalhn htis estai panti tw law",
      "11": "etecqh umin shmeron swthr os estin cristos kurios en polei daueid",
      "12": "touto umin shmeion eurhsete brefos esparganwmenon kai keimenon en fatnh",
      "13": "exaifnhs egeneto sun tw aggelw plhqos stratias ouraniou ainountwn ton qeon kai legontwn",
      "14": "en uyistois qew kai epi ghs eirhnh en anqrwpois eudokias",
      "15": "egeneto ws aphlqon ap autwn eis ton ouranon oi aggeloi oi poimenes elaloun pros allhlous dielqwmen dh ews bhqleem kai idwmen to rhma touto to gegonos o o kurios egnwrisen hmin",
      "16": "hlqan speusantes kai aneuran thn te mariam kai ton iwshf kai to brefos keimenon en th fatnh",
      "17": "de egnwrisan peri tou rhmatos tou lalhqentos autois peri tou paidiou toutou",
      "18": "pantes oi akousantes eqaumasan peri twn lalhqentwn upo twn poimenwn pros autous",
      "19": "de maria panta sunethrei ta rhmata tauta sunballousa en th kardia auths",
      "20": "upestreyan oi poimenes doxazontes kai ainountes ton qeon epi pasin ois hkousan kai eidon kaqws elalhqh pros autous",
      "21": "ote eplhsqhsan hmerai oktw tou peritemein auton kai eklhqh to onoma autou ihsous to klhqen upo tou aggelou pro tou sullhmfqhnai auton en th koilia",
      "22": "ote eplhsqhsan ai hmerai tou kaqarismou autwn kata ton nomon mwusews anhgagon auton eis ierosoluma parasthsai tw kuriw",
      "23": "gegraptai en nomw kuriou oti pan arsen dianoigon mhtran agion tw kuriw klhqhsetai",
      "24": "tou dounai qusian kata to eirhmenon en tw nomw kuriou zeugos trugonwn h duo nossous peristerwn",
      "25": "idou anqrwpos hn en ierousalhm w onoma sumewn kai o anqrwpos outos dikaios kai eulabhs prosdecomenos paraklhsin tou israhl kai pneuma hn agion ep auton",
      "26": "hn autw kecrhmatismenon upo tou pneumatos tou agiou mh idein qanaton prin h an idh ton criston kuriou",
      "27": "hlqen en tw pneumati eis to ieron kai en tw eisagagein tous goneis to paidion ihsoun tou poihsai autous kata to eiqismenon tou nomou peri autou",
      "28": "autos edexato auto eis tas agkalas kai euloghsen ton qeon kai eipen",
      "29": "apolueis ton doulon sou despota kata to rhma sou en eirhnh",
      "30": "eidon oi ofqalmoi mou to swthrion sou",
      "31": "htoimasas kata proswpon pantwn twn lawn",
      "32": "eis apokaluyin eqnwn kai doxan laou sou israhl",
      "33": "hn o pathr autou kai h mhthr qaumazontes epi tois laloumenois peri autou",
      "34": "euloghsen autous sumewn kai eipen pros mariam thn mhtera autou idou outos keitai eis ptwsin kai anastasin pollwn en tw israhl kai eis shmeion antilegomenon",
      "35": "sou de auths thn yuchn dieleusetai romfaia opws an apokalufqwsin ek pollwn kardiwn dialogismoi",
      "36": "hn anna profhtis qugathr fanouhl ek fulhs ashr auth probebhkuia en hmerais pollais zhsasa meta andros eth epta apo ths parqenias auths",
