      "13": "de eipen pros autous mhden pleon para to diatetagmenon umin prassete",
      "14": "de auton kai strateuomenoi legontes ti poihswmen kai hmeis kai eipen autois mhdena diaseishte mhde sukofanthshte kai arkeisqe tois oywniois umwn",
      "15": "de tou laou kai dialogizomenwn pantwn en tais kardiais autwn peri tou iwanou mh pote autos eih o cristos",
      "16": "legwn pasin o iwanhs egw men udati baptizw umas ercetai de o iscuroteros mou ou ouk eimi ikanos lusai ton imanta twn upodhmatwn autou autos umas baptisei en pneumati agiw kai puri",
      "17": "to ptuon en th ceiri autou diakaqarai thn alwna autou kai sunagagein ton siton eis thn apoqhkhn autou to de acuron katakausei puri asbestw",
      "18": "men oun kai etera parakalwn euhggelizeto ton laon",
