      "20": "kai touto epi pasin katekleisen ton iwanhn en fulakh",
      "21": "de en tw baptisqhnai apanta ton laon kai ihsou baptisqentos kai proseucomenou anewcqhnai ton ouranon",
      "22": "katabhnai to pneuma to agion swmatikw eidei ws peristeran ep auton kai fwnhn ex ouranou genesqai su ei o uios mou o agaphtos en soi eudokhsa",
      "23": "autos hn ihsous arcomenos wsei etwn triakonta wn uios ws enomizeto iwshf tou hlei",
