      "11": "tis lalei ws logia qeou ei tis diakonei ws ex iscuos hs corhgei o qeos ina en pasin doxazhtai o qeos dia ihsou cristou w estin h doxa kai to kratos eis tous aiwnas twn aiwnwn amhn",
      "12": "mh xenizesqe th en umin purwsei pros peirasmon umin ginomenh ws xenou umin sumbainontos",
      "13": "kaqo koinwneite tois tou cristou paqhmasin cairete ina kai en th apokaluyei ths doxhs autou carhte agalliwmenoi",
      "14": "oneidizesqe en onomati cristou makarioi oti to ths doxhs kai to tou qeou pneuma ef umas anapauetai",
