      "5": "newteroi upotaghte presbuterois pantes de allhlois thn tapeinofrosunhn egkombwsasqe oti o qeos uperhfanois antitassetai tapeinois de didwsin carin",
      "6": "oun upo thn krataian ceira tou qeou ina umas uywsh en kairw",
      "7": "thn merimnan umwn epiriyantes ep auton oti autw melei peri umwn",
