      "24": "o hkousate ap archs en umin menetw ean en umin meinh o ap archs hkousate kai umeis en tw uiw kai en tw patri meneite",
      "25": "auth estin h epaggelia hn autos ephggeilato hmin thn zwhn thn aiwnion",
      "26": "egraya umin peri twn planwntwn umas",
      "27": "umeis to crisma o elabete ap autou menei en umin kai ou creian ecete ina tis didaskh umas all ws to autou crisma didaskei umas peri pantwn kai alhqes estin kai ouk estin yeudos kai kaqws edidaxen umas menete en autw",
      "28": "nun teknia menete en autw ina ean fanerwqh scwmen parrhsian kai mh aiscunqwmen ap autou en th parousia autou",
