      "10": "toutw fanera estin ta tekna tou qeou kai ta tekna tou diabolou pas o mh poiwn dikaiosunhn ouk estin ek tou qeou kai o mh agapwn ton adelfon autou",
      "11": "auth estin h aggelia hn hkousate ap archs ina agapwmen allhlous",
      "12": "kaqws kain ek tou ponhrou hn kai esfaxen ton adelfon autou kai carin tinos esfaxen auton oti ta erga autou ponhra hn ta de tou adelfou autou dikaia",
      "13": "qaumazete adelfoi ei misei umas o kosmos",
      "14": "oidamen oti metabebhkamen ek tou qanatou eis thn zwhn oti agapwmen tous adelfous o mh agapwn menei en tw qanatw",
      "15": "o miswn ton adelfon autou anqrwpoktonos estin kai oidate oti pas anqrwpoktonos ouk ecei zwhn aiwnion en autw menousan",
      "16": "toutw egnwkamen thn agaphn oti ekeinos uper hmwn thn yuchn autou eqhken kai hmeis ofeilomen uper twn adelfwn tas yucas qeinai",
      "17": "d an ech ton bion tou kosmou kai qewrh ton adelfon autou creian econta kai kleish ta splagcna autou ap autou pws h agaph tou qeou menei en autw",
      "18": "mh agapwmen logw mhde th glwssh alla en ergw kai alhqeia",
      "19": "toutw gnwsomeqa oti ek ths alhqeias esmen kai emprosqen autou peisomen thn kardian hmwn",
