      "10": "touto ean elqw upomnhsw autou ta erga a poiei logois ponhrois fluarwn hmas kai mh arkoumenos epi toutois oute autos epidecetai tous adelfous kai tous boulomenous kwluei kai ek ths ekklhsias ekballei",
      "11": "mh mimou to kakon alla to agaqon o agaqopoiwn ek tou qeou estin o kakopoiwn ouc ewraken ton qeon",
