      "7": "sodoma kai gomorra kai ai peri autas poleis ton omoion tropon toutois ekporneusasai kai apelqousai opisw sarkos eteras prokeintai deigma puros aiwniou dikhn upecousai",
      "8": "mentoi kai outoi enupniazomenoi sarka men miainousin kuriothta de aqetousin doxas de blasfhmousin",
      "9": "de micahl o arcaggelos ote tw diabolw diakrinomenos dielegeto peri tou mwusews swmatos ouk etolmhsen krisin epenegkein blasfhmias alla eipen epitimhsai soi kurios",
      "10": "de osa men ouk oidasin blasfhmousin osa de fusikws ws ta aloga zwa epistantai en toutois fqeirontai",
      "11": "autois oti th odw tou kain eporeuqhsan kai th planh tou balaam misqou execuqhsan kai th antilogia tou kore apwlonto",
