      "23": "ek puros arpazontes ous de eleate en fobw misountes kai ton apo ths sarkos espilwmenon citwna",
      "24": "de dunamenw fulaxai umas aptaistous kai sthsai katenwpion ths doxhs autou amwmous en agalliasei",
      "25": "qew swthri hmwn dia ihsou cristou tou kuriou hmwn doxa megalwsunh kratos kai exousia pro pantos tou aiwnos kai nun kai eis pantas tous aiwnas amhn"
