      "10": "fobou a melleis pascein idou mellei ballein o diabolos ex umwn eis fulakhn ina peirasqhte kai exete qliyin hmerwn deka ginou pistos acri qanatou kai dwsw soi ton stefanon ths zwhs",
      "11": "ecwn ous akousatw ti to pneuma legei tais ekklhsiais o nikwn ou mh adikhqh ek tou qanatou tou deuterou",
      "12": "tw aggelw ths en pergamw ekklhsias grayon tade legei o ecwn thn romfaian thn distomon thn oxeian",
      "13": "pou katoikeis opou o qronos tou satana kai krateis to onoma mou kai ouk hrnhsw thn pistin mou kai en tais hmerais antipas o martus mou o pistos mou os apektanqh par umin opou o satanas katoikei",
      "14": "ecw kata sou oliga oti eceis ekei kratountas thn didachn balaam os edidasken tw balak balein skandalon enwpion twn uiwn israhl fagein eidwloquta kai porneusai",
