      "18": "tw aggelw ths en quateirois ekklhsias grayon tade legei o uios tou qeou o ecwn tous ofqalmous autou ws floga puros kai oi podes autou omoioi calkolibanw",
      "19": "sou ta erga kai thn agaphn kai thn pistin kai thn diakonian kai thn upomonhn sou kai ta erga sou ta escata pleiona twn prwtwn",
      "20": "ecw kata sou oti afeis thn gunaika iezabel h legousa eauthn profhtin kai didaskei kai plana tous emous doulous porneusai kai fagein eidwloquta",
      "21": "edwka auth cronon ina metanohsh kai ou qelei metanohsai ek ths porneias auths",
